snippet.title: Horrifying cursed head chasing after me... [HEX BOTS]
snippet.description:
Another PSX style horror game ➡️ https://youtu.be/8NzzneWUWZE

This indie horror game will scare the soul out of anyone playing it. You've gotta collect pieces of wire to insert into several computers to power them up. Power up all computers to open the escape. This would be okay if there wasn't a giant floating head watching you and trying to kill you...

Inspired by Garry's mods Nextbots. Free-to-play on itchio
